<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Afrihub</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css">

<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 28px;
font-family: "Lucida Console", Monaco, monospace;
font-size: 8px;
letter-spacing: 2px;
word-spacing: 0.6px;
color: #000000;
font-weight: 700;
text-decoration: none;
font-style: italic;
font-variant: normal;
text-transform: none;
}

.header {
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  padding: 30px;
  text-align: center;
}

#navbar {
  overflow: hidden;
  background-color: #333;
}

#navbar a {
  float: left;
  display: block;
  color: #f2f2f2;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 14px 16px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-size: 17px;
}

#navbar a:hover {
  background-color: #ddd;
  color: black;
}

#navbar a.active {
  background-color: #4CAF50;
  color: white;
}

.content {
  padding: 16px;
}

.sticky {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0;
  width: 100%;
}

.topnav .search-container {
  float: right;
}

.topnav input[type=text] {
  padding: 6px;
  margin-top: 8px;
  font-size: 17px;
  border: none;
}

.topnav .search-container button {
  float: right;
  padding: 6px 10px;
  margin-top: 8px;
  margin-right: 16px;
  background: #ddd;
  font-size: 17px;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.topnav .search-container button:hover {
  background: #ccc;
}

.sticky + .content {
  padding-top: 60px;
}

.wrapper {
  position: relative;
}
.overlay {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  width: 100%;
  background: rgba(50, 50, 50, 0.5);
}

.search-background img {
    width: 100%;
}

</style>


<body>
    <div class="container">
        <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-offset-0">
<div class="panel panel-default">
                        <div class="panel-body">

	<h2> <font color="green"> About us: </h2></font>
	<p> We are an online Tech hub where people can find and advertise skills, goods, services and expertise in computers and information technology sector. It is a place where you can interact with and find software programmers, database administrators, web designers, game developers, system analysts, cisqo and hardware specialists, computer technicians and tech solutions in Nigeria.</p>

	<p>You can find computer programmers, web designers, database administrators from anywhere in Nigeria, Africa and North-America to source your source-code production at cheap and affordable rates. </p>


	<h3> <font color="green"> Our Goal: </h3></font>
	<p> We focus on bringing computer software, and technology solutions closer to ordinary people, small-time business establishments, co-operations, organizations and institutions. We focus on becoming the No.1 place for technology solutions in Nigeria, and Africa. </p> 

    </div>
    </div>
    </div>


    </div>
<%- include('partials/footer') %> 
</body>
